{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:30.727106+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: e1fb26cc4bb77a7e3f333f8d5babdd2b3b3b923b)", "id": "lc_55f1bd19-121b-46f3-9184-ba7aaf4943d2"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import { createPinia } from 'pinia'\nimport { createApp } from 'vue'\nimport Default from '@/layouts/default/Default.vue'\nimport App from './App.vue'\nimport { router } from './router'\n\nconst app = createApp(App)\n\napp.component('LayoutDefault', Default)\napp.use(createPinia())\napp.use(router)\n\napp.mount('#app')\n", "id": "lc_70aafcb9-c4fd-4bf7-85d3-03bcbff22d54"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "e09effcd-edb8-4ae3-866e-8bc2a80ada54", "tool_call_id": "call_7c337214d0894c3cbd01a7df", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:30.728054+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 4d6c36b307bc51212a1a105cb8a8092b5cb70929)", "id": "lc_0e884476-d204-4385-8cc7-7ad8ce369032"}, {"type": "text", "text": "<template>\n  <component :is=\"layout\">\n    <RouterView />\n  </component>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nimport '@/scss/app.scss'\n\nexport default {\n  name: 'App',\n  computed: {\n    layout() {\n      return `layout-${this.$route.meta.layout || 'default'}`\n    },\n  },\n}\n</script>\n", "id": "lc_8e02f6a6-0efd-466f-8390-bea17a19df8c"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "5196859f-d9e4-467e-9587-97aa30c9657f", "tool_call_id": "call_43613c68e9de4eb9827195e1", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:30.728686+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 8f0fb941d50dbdb6233ecf221771bdf5425016bf)", "id": "lc_0d90c1db-c97f-4bb9-9182-d087750cd5dc"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import { createRouter, createWebHashHistory } from 'vue-router'\nimport Home from '../views/Home.vue'\n\nconst history = createWebHashHistory()\nconst routes = [\n  {\n    path: '/',\n    name: 'Home',\n    component: Home,\n    meta: {\n      layout: 'default',\n    },\n  },\n  {\n    path: '/about',\n    name: 'About',\n    // route level code-splitting\n    // this generates a separate chunk (about.[hash].js) for this route\n    // which is lazy-loaded when the route is visited.\n    component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: \"about\" */ '../views/About.vue'),\n    meta: {\n      layout: 'default',\n    },\n  },\n]\nconst router = createRouter({\n  linkActiveClass: 'active',\n  history,\n  routes,\n})\n\nexport { router }\n", "id": "lc_6a932a3d-00e9-48f1-ac4c-671b84f58576"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "b3ae5739-fa0d-44db-8834-a27df47ff76c", "tool_call_id": "call_548f9d9d3c8d462bad38d4dc", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:30.728769+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 79ab8c039c4c3d3a54677f692f847917ad9dc553)", "id": "lc_ee3f2439-ad0b-4c5b-83d2-44edc41f2d30"}, {"type": "text", "text": "<template>\n  <div class=\"default-page-wrapper\">\n    <DefaultNav />\n    <slot />\n    <DefaultFooter />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport DefaultFooter from './DefaultFooter.vue'\nimport DefaultNav from './DefaultNav.vue'\n\ndefineOptions({\n  name: 'DefaultLayout',\n})\n</script>\n\n<style lang=\"scss\">\n/* Sticky footer */\nhtml {\n  position: relative;\n  min-height: 100%;\n}\nbody {\n  margin-bottom: 60px; /* Margin bottom equal to footer height */\n}\n.default-page-wrapper {\n  padding: 5em 0em 3em 0em;\n}\n.footer {\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 60px; /* Footer height */\n  line-height: 60px; /* Vertically center the text */\n  background-color: $gray-100;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n</style>\n", "id": "lc_dad4ee16-d484-4086-8736-8754b99b1d6e"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "af936ed0-540e-4a5e-8b50-1c6e0874e0f1", "tool_call_id": "call_ac0044ff9cdd4953bcb1841b", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:39.939686+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's how the app bootstraps routing and layout rendering, and how the About page is loaded:\n\n---\n\n## Bootstrapping\n\n**`src/main.js`** is the entry point. It:\n\n1. Creates the Vue app with `createApp(App)`.\n2. **Registers the default layout globally** as the component `LayoutDefault`:\n   ```js\n   app.component('LayoutDefault', Default)\n   ```\n   This is key — it makes the `Default.vue` layout available by the name `layout-default`, which the App component resolves dynamically.\n3. Installs Pinia (state management) and the Vue Router.\n4. Mounts the app to `#app` (defined in `index.html`).\n\n---\n\n## Routing\n\n**`src/router/index.js`** sets up a **hash-based** router (`createWebHashHistory`) with two routes:\n\n| Path      | Name    | Component | Loading    |\n|-----------|---------|-----------|------------|\n| `/`       | `Home`  | `Home.vue` | **Eager** — imported statically at the top of the file. |\n| `/about`  | `About` | `About.vue` | **Lazy** — loaded on-demand via a dynamic `import()`. |\n\nBoth routes carry `meta: { layout: 'default' }`, which tells the App component which layout wrapper to use.\n\n---\n\n## Layout Rendering\n\n**`src/App.vue`** is the root component. Its template is:\n\n```html\n<component :is=\"layout\">\n  <RouterView />\n</component>\n```\n\nIt computes `layout` dynamically from the current route's metadata:\n\n```js\ncomputed: {\n  layout() {\n    return `layout-${this.$route.meta.layout || 'default'}`\n  },\n}\n```\n\nSo when a route has `meta: { layout: 'default' }`, Vue resolves `<component :is=\"layout-default\">` to the globally-registered `LayoutDefault` component.\n\n**`src/layouts/default/Default.vue`** then renders the page structure:\n\n```html\n<div class=\"default-page-wrapper\">\n  <DefaultNav />      <!-- navigation bar -->\n  <slot />            <!-- page content injected here -->\n  <DefaultFooter />   <!-- sticky footer -->\n</div>\n```\n\nThe `<slot />` is where the matched route component (e.g., `Home.vue` or `About.vue`) gets rendered — that's what `<RouterView />` provides as a child of the layout.\n\n---\n\n## How the About Page is Loaded\n\n1. The user navigates to `#/about`.\n2. The router matches the `/about` route.\n3. Because `component` is a **dynamic `import()`**, the browser fetches a separate chunk (`about.[hash].js`) only at this point — this is **route-level code splitting**.\n4. Vue renders `App.vue` → resolves `meta.layout === 'default'` → renders `LayoutDefault` (with nav + footer) → places the resolved `About.vue` component into the layout's `<slot />`.\n\nThe `About.vue` view itself is minimal — just a `<div class=\"container\"><h1>This is the about page</h1></div>`.\n\n---\n\n**In summary:** The app uses a dynamic `<component :is=\"...\">` pattern in `App.vue` to swap layouts based on route metadata, combined with Vue Router's lazy loading to split the About page into its own chunk for efficient loading.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 741, "prompt_tokens": 8629, "total_tokens": 9370, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 23, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 7488, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0003881864, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001807064, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00020748}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871250-zr4ZWgY0OeQKggyleVnT", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea432-c329-74d1-b7c9-744793978e4b-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadat